Uses of Interface
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.RoboflowResponseData

Packages that use RoboflowResponseData
Package
Description
nusri.fyp.demo.dto
This package contains Data Transfer Object (DTO) classes used for transferring data between different layers of the application, such as between controllers and services.
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data
The nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data package contains the data models used to represent both request and response structures for interacting with the Roboflow API.
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.response
This package contains the response classes used to map the data received from the Roboflow API.
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.request
This package contains classes responsible for constructing and sending HTTP requests to the Roboflow API.
